        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "1. Overview"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "usp_ReadingScheduleManualBilling_Select",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to retrieve records from the "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "ManualBill.ReadingScheduleManualBilling",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " table. It filters these records based on specific criteria related to invoice account groups and billing cycles. The procedure also joins with the "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Billing.ApplicationTimeFrame",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " table to ensure that only records from the current processing period are selected."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
